claim.claim-text:
9. A polymer nozzle for electrospray ionization, comprising:
a support structure, formed of a silicon material;
a MEMS electrospray nozzle structure, having an exterior portion, and a hollow interior portion, having a first nozzle part which is supported by said silicon support structure, and a second nozzle part which extends beyond said support structure and forms a freestanding part, said nozzle structure being flexible.
